    <th align="left" scope="row"><textarea name="FAQ" cols="120" rows="30" readonly="readonly" id="FAQ"> REGISTRATION AND SIGN IN :

1. How do I register with Omega Theatre?
Click on the 'Register' link on the homepage of omegatheatre.com. Enter your full name, Email id., contact number, password and click on 'Submit' and you are registered with us.

2. Is it necessary to register for booking tickets?
Yes, it is necessary to register on the site to book tickets.

3. What are the benefits of registering on the site?
By registering, you get access to your booking history on the site. You can also opt to get information on special offers. You can also set up favorite cinemas to get instant show times each time you login.

A. TICKET BOOKING :

a) Before booking Tickets :

1. When does advance booking open on Omega Theatre?
The advance booking facility is directly controlled by the cinema. Whenever the cinema opens the show for advance booking, the show is automatically made available on Omega theatre. We also have the facility of pre-book for big movies. Please check this section for advance bookings of movies weeks in advance.
2. Do you charge extra fees for a booking?
No, you only have to pay for each ticket that you book.

3. Can I choose my seat at the cinema?
Yes, this is one of the most important features we offer. You have the choice of selecting or changing your seats at every step of the transaction. This facility is available to only those venues that support this feature.

4. How many tickets can I book in one transaction?
You can book as many tickets which are available at the time you does your booking.

5. Is there a telephone number where I can contact you and book my tickets?
For contact details goto to contact tab in the home page.

6. Is there a cut off time for booking tickets?
The cut-off time for booking may vary from cinema to cinema as it is governed by the cinema. Itâ€™s usually 24 hours before the show start time.

b) During Booking Tickets :

1. How can I confirm whether my tickets have been booked?
When a booking is confirmed, an email is automatically sent to you with the booking details

c) After Booking Tickets:

1. Will my tickets be delivered after my booking is done?
No. Your tickets are confirmed and paid for, and delivery is not necessary. You can visit the cinema at any time before the show and collect your tickets from the box office. Please note that you will be required to show the Transaction card used and sign on the acknowledgement slip while collecting the tickets.

2. Do I need to carry my Transaction card when I collect my tickets?
Yes. It is necessary to carry the Transaction card used for booking when you pick the tickets from the cinema. This is to ensure that the person booking the ticket is the bonafide owner of the card

3. Can I change my seat numbers?
No. It is not possible to change the seat numbers of a ticket once booked.
4. Can I change the show time that I have booked for?
No. It is not possible to change the show time once a ticket has been booked.

5. Can we cancel or replace our tickets?
No. As per government regulations, once a ticket has been paid for, it is deemed sold. It cannot be replaced or cancelled.

B. TROUBLESHOOTING :

1. What browser works best with Omega Theatre?
We currently support IE(version 8 or later), Firefox/Mozilla (Firefox 3 or later), Google Chrome, Apple Safari, all versions of opera and are adding support for other browsers as well.

2. Why is the speed of this website so slow?
We have optimized the website to offer the best user experience, please check your connection with your Internet Service Provider.

3. Does this site use cookies?
Cookies help us customize our site to our customers' requirements, and offer a more personalized service.

4. What do I do if my booking is not completed?
We are sorry for this unlikely inconvenience. If your booking process fails during a payment process, we will notify you if any erroneous charges have been incurred. And reverse any amount charged within 3 weeks.

